sequenceDiagram
    title Google Voice — Outgoing Call Flow
    participant Browser
    participant GV_WSS as voice.telephony.goog (SIP WebSocket)
    participant OGHP as OGHP Gateway (74.125.39.x)
    participant STUN as stun.l.google.com

    Note over Browser,GV_WSS: SIP Registration
    Browser->>GV_WSS: REGISTER sip:web.c.pbx.voice.sip.google.com
    GV_WSS-->>Browser: 401 Unauthorized (Digest challenge)
    Browser->>GV_WSS: REGISTER (with auth credentials)
    GV_WSS-->>Browser: 200 OK (registered)

    Note over Browser,OGHP: Call Setup (INVITE)
    Browser->>GV_WSS: INVITE sip:+19193718044 (SDP offer: Opus/48kHz)
    GV_WSS-->>Browser: 100 Trying
    GV_WSS-->>Browser: 183 Session Progress (SDP answer)

    Note over Browser,OGHP: Provisional Response Acknowledgment
    Browser->>GV_WSS: PRACK
    GV_WSS-->>Browser: 200 OK
    GV_WSS-->>Browser: 180 Ringing
    Browser->>GV_WSS: PRACK
    GV_WSS-->>Browser: 200 OK

    Note over Browser,STUN: ICE + DTLS Negotiation
    Browser->>STUN: STUN Binding Request (get SRFLX candidate)
    STUN-->>Browser: SRFLX 75.189.129.182:53408
    Browser->>OGHP: ICE connectivity check
    OGHP-->>Browser: ICE success
    Note over Browser,OGHP: DTLS handshake → SRTP keys derived

    Note over Browser,OGHP: Call Connected
    GV_WSS-->>Browser: 200 OK (final)
    Browser->>GV_WSS: ACK

    Note over Browser,OGHP: Bidirectional Audio (RTP/SRTP/Opus)
    Browser->>OGHP: RTP (Opus 48kHz, SRTP encrypted)
    OGHP-->>Browser: RTP (Opus 48kHz, SRTP encrypted)

    Note over Browser,GV_WSS: Call Terminated
    GV_WSS-->>Browser: BYE
    Browser->>GV_WSS: 200 OK

    %% Confidence: High — 30 SIP frames + 13 RTC events captured from live call
    %% Source: IAET browser extension capture, session 098a8b26
